---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Free Prompt Studio" description="Privacy Policy for Free Prompt Studio. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data.">
  <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-tertiary">Last updated: June 2026</p>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">1. No Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">Free Prompt Studio runs entirely in your browser. We do not collect, store, or process any personal data. No analytics, no cookies (beyond localStorage for theme preference), and no tracking.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">2. Local Storage</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We use localStorage to remember your theme preference (light/dark mode) and banner dismissal state. This data stays on your device and is never sent to any server. You can clear it at any time via your browser settings.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">3. No Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We do not embed third-party analytics, ads, or tracking scripts. The only external resources are fonts loaded from Google Fonts and the Astro/Vite build assets.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">4. URL Sharing</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">The "Share URL" feature encodes prompt data into the URL hash using Base64. This data is not transmitted to us. It stays in your browser's address bar and is only shared when you copy and send the URL to someone else.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We may update this policy. Changes will be reflected on this page.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">6. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">For questions about this policy, please open an issue on our GitHub repository.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
